    <summary>Quba-Viewer is a cross platform open source application to display structured (i.e., XML) and hybrid (Factur-X/ZUGFeRD PDF) electronic invoices.
Documentation-wise there is a doc RE Architecture, Development, Debugging and testing in general and some Electron and E-Invoice peculiarities like interprocess (IPC) communication, XSLT and codelists in particular.</summary>
